description: 90 degree leg bend, laying on your back, sit up until elbows are passed your knees.
Arms at your side, bend so your elbows so they remain close to your body and lower your body until close to the floor.
Lift made from a standing position without the aid of bench.
While seated, you pull a hanging bar toward you to reach chin level, then release it back up.
Utilising a rowing machine to simulate the rowing action.
